    "body" : "<p>Draemon is correct. You can also declare <code>m</code> as taking <a href=\"http://java.sun.com/j2se/1.5.0/docs/guide/language/varargs.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><em>varargs</em></a>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>void m(String... strs) {\n    // strs is seen as a normal String[] inside the method\n}\n\nm(\"blah\", \"hey\", \"yo\"); // no [] or {} needed; each string is a separate arg here\n</code></pre>\n"
