      "body" : "Possibly useful point: You can&#39;t do this with primitives. You&#39;ll end up with a single-element <code>List</code> of <code>type[]</code> where <code>type</code> is that primitive. e.g. <code>Arrays.asList([some ints])</code> results in a <code>List&lt;int[]&gt;</code>."
