    "body" : "<p>Another way to do that, if you want the result as a List inline, you can do it like this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Arrays.asList(new String[] { \"String1\", \"string2\" });\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 1782862,
      "reputation" : 569,
      "user_id" : 1625126,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/XFXuU.jpg?s=256",
