    "answer_id" : 44903150,
    "question_id" : 1154008,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can create a method somewhere</p>\n\n<pre><code>public static &lt;T&gt; T[] toArray(T... ts) {\n    return ts;\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>then use it</p>\n\n<pre><code>m(toArray(\"blah\", \"hey\", \"yo\"));\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>for better look.</p>\n"
  }, {
